{"tid":1990791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連兩周無本土病例　陳時中：6月底前可能告一段落","createTime":"2020-04-27T03:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T03:34:10.000Z","uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"224ebdde68a5edf9af33f76f850ea85ed8095ed8","tid":1990791,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情衝擊全球各產業，不過台灣近來國內疫情確診病例已近2周未出現本土個案，昨天還出現0確診的情形。立法院財政委員會今（27日）上午進行質詢時，國民黨立委曾銘宗問到，國內疫情是否在6月底以前告一段落？衛福部長陳時中回應，有這樣可能。不過，到今年秋冬抗體、藥物和疫苗研發無法產生效果，那在今年秋冬疫情恢復的可能性相對高。 &nbsp;&nbsp; 此外，曾銘宗還問到，針對社交距離的模式，是否維持到年底或明年？陳時中說，這是需要常態化。疫苗和藥物研發，需要精確的科學驗證，目前看起來是有一點跡象。曾銘宗追問，是社交距離常態化短則維持2、3年，長則維持更長？陳時中說，需要看藥物、疫苗研發速度與情況。"},{"pid":"53b94d955283e156393e8f510125535d9b291914","tid":1990791,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200427/AEIZ3FT5HXDXTQ4YGRGPQSL7BA/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200427%2FAEIZ3FT5HXDXTQ4YGRGPQSL7BA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=89af117b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200427%2FAEIZ3FT5HXDXTQ4YGRGPQSL7BA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=70e962c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200427/AEIZ3FT5HXDXTQ4YGRGPQSL7BA/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"89b9fd1e3d44304861ae6c6cecd3725992eddffc","tid":1990791,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/